documentation artifacts described below) is licensed under the MIT License above.

The **data artifacts, dataset/model cards, schema documentation, and benchmark
methodology** — primarily the contents of `data/`, `docs/`, and `data/schema/`
— are licensed under **Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International
(CC-BY-4.0)**. See `LICENSE-DATA` for the full text.

Third-party datasets (mcPHASES via PhysioNet, NHANES via CDC) remain under their
own respective licenses and data use agreements and are NOT redistributed here.
Only derived, de-identified, aggregated artifacts (or small synthetic samples)
